title: A.Midsummer.Nights.Rave[2002]
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0323248/maindetails" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0323248/maindetails</a>

Shakespeare's A MIDSUMMER NIGHT'S DREAM gets a rave culture makeover in this energetic and funny adaptation set at an all night druggy dance party. After sunset, a group of Los Angeles friends are given a dose of a glowing green "love potion" by their party boy pal, Puck. As the evening unfolds, the gang's lack of inhibitions will allow them to connect with the boys and girls of their dreams and become one with the music. But will a soured drug deal ruin their collective high? Andrew Keegan (10 THINGS I HATE ABOUT YOU) stars in this energetic slice of comedic decadence set to a pulsating beat.
